    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within 15% of experimental values across the COU operating envelope. The assessment team notes that validation simulations were executed under solver build 2026-q1-build-7-rc2 rather than the released build 2026-q1-build-7; vendor confirmation indicates the builds are functionally identical, with the only difference being installer metadata. The team accepted this equivalence argument without re-running validation under the released build. COU1 credibility assessment accepted for regulatory submission.",
